<h2 class="header"><i>10</i>Question 10<a class="headerlink" href="#question-10" name="question-10">&para;</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Write down five non-isomorphic groups of order 8. (You do not need to show that these groups are non-isomorphic.)</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span>$\mathbb Z/8\mathbb Z$</span>, <span>$\mathbb Z/2 \mathbb Z \times \mathbb Z/2 \mathbb Z \times \mathbb Z/2 \mathbb Z$</span>, <span>$\mathbb Z/2 \mathbb Z \times \mathbb Z/4 \mathbb Z$</span>, the dihedral group <span>$D_8$</span>, the quaternion group (no idea what this is but it was mentioned during a tutorial).</p>
